Race.SpecificTitle: Fifth Ward FPD #1 -- 15 Mills - PJ - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Fifth Ward Fire Protection District No. 1 Proposition
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Fifth Ward Fire Protection District No. 1 of St. Helena Parish, Louisiana (the "District"), continue to levy a special tax of fifteen (15) mills on all property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $89,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2015 and ending with the year 2024, for the purpose of acquiring, constructing, improving, maintaining and/or operating fire protection facilities, vehicles and/or equipment, including both movable and immoveable property, to be used, directly or indirectly, by the District to provide fire protection service?

Race.SpecificTitle: S. 2nd Wd. FPD -- 10 Mills - PJ - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
South Second Ward Fire Protection District Proposition
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall South Second Ward Fire Protection District of St. Helena Parish, Louisiana (the "District"), continue to levy a special tax of ten (10) mills on all property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $30,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2015 and ending with the year 2024, for the purpose of acquiring, constructing, improving, maintaining and/or operating fire protection facilities, vehicles and/or equipment, including both movable and immovable property, to be used, directly or indirectly, by the District to provide fire protection service?

Race.SpecificTitle: Sub-Rd. Dist#2 of Rd. Dist#2 Prop.#1 -- 10 Mills - PJ - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Sub-Road District Number Two of Road District Number Two Propositions
Proposition No. 1
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Sub-Road District Number Two of Road District Number Two of St. Helena Parish (the "District"), continue to levy a special tax of ten (10) mills on all property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $55,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2015 and ending with the year 2024, for the purpose of building, rebuilding, resurfacing, maintaining and keeping in repair the public roads, highways and bridges in the District?

Race.SpecificTitle: Sub-Rd. Dist#2 of Rd. Dist#2 Prop.#2 -- 6 Mills - PJ - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Sub-Road District Number Two of Road District Number Two Propositions
Proposition No. 2
(Millage Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Sub-Road District Number Two of Road District Number Two of St. Helena Parish (the "District"), continue to levy a special tax of six (6) mills on all property subject to taxation in the District (an estimated $33,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2016 and ending with the year 2025, for the purpose of building, rebuilding, resurfacing, maintaining and keeping in repair the public roads, highways and bridges of the District?
